name: Arithmetic - The Orange Theory
description:
Arithmetic - The Orange Theory is a continuation of the Number Theory series.
This is an interactive NFT, an ever-changing art. They were designed by hand and developed with code. Click/tap the picture to change the image. 

Using a computer, you can click the 'space' bar to create a new image; press the 's' to save it. There is almost zero chance to make two same one.
